<body>
    <h1>T6 - Requirement Analysis Document</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"9c2206aeb1ad" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-=
1.Introduction">1. Introduction</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"1b1f5e945c42" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.1Purpo=
se">1.1 Purpose</h2>
<p local-id=3D"a41cb678e0ca">The purpose of this document is to define and =
analyze the functional and non-functional requirements for deploying two st=
atic frontend applications on an Apache web server using personalized subdo=
mains and securing them with Let=E2=80=99s Encrypt SSL certificates.</p>
<p local-id=3D"b03ca20868c3">This document is intended for:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"02b7cd277173">
<li local-id=3D"41a38c7746a2">
<p local-id=3D"d82738b295ad">Project Mentors</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"236cacbb693e">
<p local-id=3D"41b6cac3f5ff">DevOps Engineers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ca60517c943d">
<p local-id=3D"b2509961419c">Solution Architects</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3a70a074795e">
<p local-id=3D"2614dfe1e581">Technical Reviewers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c80b24c1d38e">
<p local-id=3D"dd00b4587597">Stakeholders</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"079a7e5609f1">It ensures clarity of scope, requirements, con=
straints, and validation criteria for the deployment task.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"36aa90f58c53">
<h2 local-id=3D"e4d6b7c6a4b5" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.2Scope=
">1.2 Scope</h2>
<p local-id=3D"dc49cb823263">This project includes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"c80ae7ece001">
<li local-id=3D"0928a2c285db">
<p local-id=3D"02b63bcfde32">Installation and configuration of Apache on Ub=
untu</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"de95f1586e2f">
<p local-id=3D"1989adea3aa7">Deployment of two static frontend applications=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3acbdbcbe02b">
<p local-id=3D"2d14fb2555f6">Subdomain-based hosting</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b1b05d568b29">
<p local-id=3D"7cbc4690f730">DNS A record configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4f1556780e4e">
<p local-id=3D"52e256df7b6b">SSL implementation using Let=E2=80=99s Encrypt=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c5e603f4f3d0">
<p local-id=3D"b9c758ca922d">HTTPS enforcement</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e87dc116909e">
<p local-id=3D"93e9b99dec70">SSL auto-renewal validation</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"d1b110806327">This project does not include:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"fa914da47a10">
<li local-id=3D"3abd7489d87d">
<p local-id=3D"faf95cde8b3e">CI/CD pipeline setup</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ae338f643d8f">
<p local-id=3D"e6d463fa87dd">Containerization (Docker/Kubernetes)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f249caf5fd56">
<p local-id=3D"3bd88ba4f4bf">Load balancing</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8b1481805031">
<p local-id=3D"b2875f9d36de">Monitoring tools implementation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"278c2fcae1ab">
<p local-id=3D"a2241f9f6a6f">Backend integration</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d5cd9843c016">
<h2 local-id=3D"cce56fbf7d9f" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.3Defin=
itions,Acronyms,andAbbreviations">1.3 Definitions, Acronyms, and Abbreviati=
ons</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"29=
86f4aa-878c-4819-ad64-33595275be03" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"8a699c84cbbc">
<th data-local-id=3D"816c71a086b5" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"f56d065a4503">Term</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"efeb40e5924a" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"c7c203391348">Definition</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"612747b43e29">
<td data-local-id=3D"3631d3c6bc9f" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"da4dd56029b7">EC2</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"78f439f36143" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7a27b2d4870d">Elastic Compute Cloud (AWS Virtual Server)</p>=
</td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"72d68604e63b">
<td data-local-id=3D"15e4edf8bae6" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7c2fd3f75dff">Apache</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"71f8c5a75280" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f0a2b0b26db4">Open-source web server software</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"5ec121d45d93">
<td data-local-id=3D"1d73e3109318" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"669754fe171e">DNS</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"51688874008c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d1ab23161fb2">Domain Name System</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"58bbd052f79c">
