<p local-id=3D"a333e1f36deb">SSL</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"1ef4fcae5fd1" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"68d2a936a0a9">Secure Sockets Layer</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"9513f101b12b">
<td data-local-id=3D"6cf346783b86" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"614b1788c2af">TLS</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e8365d480fbb" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9dabdd24031a">Transport Layer Security</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"2471acb16f5b">
<td data-local-id=3D"5ad6ef04bec9" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"eeab9f2904c7">Certbot</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"2e79ac744048" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"832adbde0f13">Tool used to obtain and manage SSL certificate=
s</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"93fcf625cc39">
<td data-local-id=3D"874311de6dad" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a76d62b10c8b">Virtual Host</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"86aee0d6a963" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d6eae021d76f">Apache configuration to host multiple domains<=
/p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"8190f0f194a0">
<td data-local-id=3D"0d84c4cea861" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"397c8f87520c">HTTPS</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9888461692f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ff7e1b644486">Secure version of HTTP</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"8b4ad9f8f92b">
<h2 local-id=3D"7566e4f9dc23" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.4Refer=
ences">1.4 References</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"b1af4cae8545">
<li local-id=3D"8415fd781939">
<p local-id=3D"68b8f42e962a">Repository: <a href=3D"https://github.com/push=
kar-iamops/frontend-apps" local-id=3D"3f1d998b4ff7" data-card-appearance=3D=
"inline" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://github.com/pushka=
r-iamops/frontend-apps</a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fdb96ad22a9d">
<p local-id=3D"bd247ba16283">DigitalOcean Guide: How To Secure Apache with =
Let=E2=80=99s Encrypt on Ubuntu</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"755ed7999b1e">
<p local-id=3D"27b2d04f4a19">Let=E2=80=99s Encrypt Official Documentation</=
p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d82c3ad0b23c">
<h2 local-id=3D"2efb99764dfb" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.5Overv=
iew">1.5 Overview</h2>
<p local-id=3D"9442a22fdad6">This document outlines:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"b67aa45e7415">
<li local-id=3D"5ff9c6b5bf36">
<p local-id=3D"f6e53fb07607">Project objectives</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"89e97197c0bf">
<p local-id=3D"56085b74e083">Functional and non-functional requirements</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"e8d89dcdd398">
<p local-id=3D"de7466baccf2">Constraints and risks</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fdd87302f902">
<p local-id=3D"0f80da5fe555">Assumptions and dependencies</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"30f64970a842">
<p local-id=3D"1cbc52d2fb91">Security and performance expectations</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d830a1149fa4">
<h1 local-id=3D"72967a444a80" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.Projec=
tOverview">2. Project Overview</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"bb50c9994872" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.1Proje=
ctObjectives">2.1 Project Objectives</h2>
<p local-id=3D"e97a36a0aa85">The primary objectives are:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"5f420395bf74">
<li local-id=3D"1c8f0e1326e0">
<p local-id=3D"1a7267b6d572">Deploy two frontend applications from the prov=
ided repository</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d6e25393c6b5">
<p local-id=3D"35ee33623647">Host each application on a personalized subdom=
ain</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"866ae4049b9d">
<p local-id=3D"223e28ac2cda">Configure Apache Virtual Hosts</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6f6d9e5097cb">
<p local-id=3D"b619b01ddc39">Implement HTTPS using Let=E2=80=99s Encrypt</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"920a5808707c">
<p local-id=3D"651102130b0b">Validate SSL auto-renewal</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"ee076c38bdf2">
<h2 local-id=3D"b479f13f36c4" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.2Busin=
essGoals">2.2 Business Goals</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"7f70e90bd2f0">
<li local-id=3D"ef3e6d677d92">
<p local-id=3D"90c672e35de0">Ensure secure web hosting</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8e33101d4e3f">
<p local-id=3D"18f58b874652">Follow industry-standard HTTPS practices</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"fc276a3a42ce">
<p local-id=3D"7bc905ac4d93">Provide structured multi-application hosting</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0af2109c1d37">
<p local-id=3D"b9be2a5f6357">Achieve zero SSL licensing cost</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a4a12d6b62ae">
<p local-id=3D"e4b6212880cd">Deliver deployment within 6 hours</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"51b02135f46a">
<h2 local-id=3D"cb108230f2ec" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.3Backg=
round">2.3 Background</h2>
<p local-id=3D"8005c7d2e105">The task was assigned to deploy static fronten=
d applications in a secure and structured manner using Apache and SSL. The =
goal was to simulate real-world production deployment using best practices =
for domain configuration and encryption.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"743cd4058a9b">
<h2 local-id=3D"6e31ec9b831d" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.4Const=
raints">2.4 Constraints</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"b1feba62b515">
<li local-id=3D"88ce56e38499">
<p local-id=3D"eabdb956b06f">Single Ubuntu EC2 instance</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0739559bc472">
<p local-id=3D"307e6f3a2ed1">Static applications only</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f81fc437d740">
<p local-id=3D"ca8222bb9e12">Time limit: 6 hours</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"392685db1bac">
<p local-id=3D"38e984415c18">No external DevOps tools allowed</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"85cdbbc24d81">
<p local-id=3D"96381d9a8804">No CI/CD integration</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"f7d5d9829813">
<h1 local-id=3D"4b4af53f2e32" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.Functi=
onalRequirements">3. Functional Requirements</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"dfedf046cfe7">
<h2 local-id=3D"587769d702af" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.1UseCa=
seDiagram">3.1 Use Case Diagram</h2>
<p local-id=3D"c9ab56419575">Actors:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ad0708379c9d">
<li local-id=3D"8fec3aae339e">
<p local-id=3D"b4ae3f80f4d0">DevOps Engineer</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6219c5099f5a">
<p local-id=3D"6008b2f3e59a">End User (Browser User)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4f201848e688">
<p local-id=3D"80afc08fca24">Apache Web Server</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"aef7cc4dc412">
<p local-id=3D"eb2f2f81b21a">Let=E2=80=99s Encrypt</p></li>
</ul><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper c=
onfluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image ima=
ge-center" alt=3D"image-20260309-182817.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy"=
 src=3D"f33c33eb3f9b9ce52432efcaf0cc56a75ce8627e22fdc84b874d411df8167e2d" d=
ata-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/179=
8373380/image-20260309-182817.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D177308=
0900159&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"721" data-width=
=3D"1121" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"18=
43527797" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"a=
ttachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20260309-182817.png"=
 data-base-url=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-c=
ontent-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1798373380" =
data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"3" data-media-id=3D"d425edf1-25ca=
-40ac-a0ea-2e74a834986c" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"300"></span>
<p local-id=3D"6a0a7a44506f"></p>
<hr local-id=3D"3cdfbb915c95">
<h2 local-id=3D"0a1c987a3fa8" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2UseCa=
ses">3.2 Use Cases</h2>
<hr local-id=3D"c1c4a8f097bc">
<h3 local-id=3D"194d524543f0" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2.1Use=
Case1:DeployFrontendApplication">3.2.1 Use Case 1: Deploy Frontend Applicat=
ion</h3>
<p local-id=3D"b2fd08d9917a"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
Deploy a static frontend application on Apache under a personalized subdoma=
in.</p>
<p local-id=3D"1013312c7f74"><strong>Actors:</strong><br>
DevOps Engineer</p>
<p local-id=3D"dd68eddfe88d"><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"1fa3a28e47cf">
<li local-id=3D"9a7d3e48ced4">
<p local-id=3D"a911bf47cd62">Ubuntu server is available</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5fa3831fe75d">
<p local-id=3D"e2c0da607ba0">Apache is installed</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"44a03a2a5cb2">
<p local-id=3D"bee0a3c866c1">DNS A record configured</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"ae339a903a13"><strong>Postconditions:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"c8d48e663b71">
<li local-id=3D"226d7ff07bb1">
<p local-id=3D"465d7dbcb0d2">Application is accessible over HTTP</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"670b87e40ef7"><strong>Flow of Events:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"282868ae3527">
<li local-id=3D"5364faad2418">
<p local-id=3D"b031e50eb70c">Clone repository</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"67f7bd7ab95a">
<p local-id=3D"6bc5fd874aee">Create directory under /var/www</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1b52e00e62f0">
<p local-id=3D"fabe40480f68">Copy application files</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b430fb2da047">
<p local-id=3D"fb0a4c15dbad">Create Virtual Host</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2542323940a7">
<p local-id=3D"8406e4a3717d">Reload Apache</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"f4123e5d4d32"><strong>Alternative Flows:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"ffb000dc2cc3">
<li local-id=3D"b9b3791ff481">
<p local-id=3D"9e88865d49ab">Apache configuration error =E2=86=92 Fix confi=
g and reload</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"decd08f64823">
<p local-id=3D"0f6be94edb55">DNS not configured =E2=86=92 Configure A recor=
d</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"68a54b3b5474">
<h3 local-id=3D"c3a25716f7f7" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2.2Use=
Case2:SecureApplicationwithSSL">3.2.2 Use Case 2: Secure Application with S=
SL</h3>
<p local-id=3D"502b3fc49e22"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
Enable HTTPS for both deployed applications using Let=E2=80=99s Encrypt.</p=
>
<p local-id=3D"ef2338399a9a"><strong>Actors:</strong><br>
DevOps Engineer<br>
Let=E2=80=99s Encrypt</p>
<p local-id=3D"e4e5368aba99"><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"28e6a881181a">
<li local-id=3D"034875e2e1a2">
<p local-id=3D"f77db4eec1d9">Application accessible over HTTP</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b9b35e5be8e0">
<p local-id=3D"9410008aee67">Port 80 open</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"94a6359ed821">
<p local-id=3D"c1194090d9af">DNS resolution working</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"13dd6ad6ffaf"><strong>Postconditions:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"ce44f09b9f54">
<li local-id=3D"5f296f4b2349">
<p local-id=3D"b15c03f5f5fe">Application accessible over HTTPS</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"24156e295532">
<p local-id=3D"180154ab5fe0">HTTP automatically redirects to HTTPS</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"b4ec602a1544"><strong>Flow of Events:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"8da2bfff042f">
<li local-id=3D"f215131e0915">
<p local-id=3D"289f68a09cd0">Install Certbot</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e1f9107fb39e">
<p local-id=3D"65e999081156">Run certbot --apache</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0b2b015dfee6">
<p local-id=3D"40ba120b752f">Select domains</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b2e2788a04d9">
<p local-id=3D"fc1472debc61">Enable HTTP to HTTPS redirect</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4ffa34120f26">
<p local-id=3D"1633668763d1">Validate secure access</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"3bbf5307c9d1"><strong>Alternative Flows:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"aab9beb5b6e9">
<li local-id=3D"b4a3ab9e7b3b">
<p local-id=3D"99ae718c097f">Port 443 blocked =E2=86=92 Open in security gr=
oup</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d0d5da8e987b">
<p local-id=3D"c62349745bd2">DNS not resolving =E2=86=92 Fix DNS</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"427e20caa084">
<h3 local-id=3D"14dba1325127" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2.3Use=
Case3:ValidateSSLAuto-Renewal">3.2.3 Use Case 3: Validate SSL Auto-Renewal<=
/h3>
<p local-id=3D"0b61d727a42e"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
Verify SSL certificate will renew automatically.</p>
<p local-id=3D"8b277e2c0c52"><strong>Actors:</strong><br>
DevOps Engineer</p>
<p local-id=3D"0debe46848ed"><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"21d3da28c93d">
<li local-id=3D"a3bad630038e">
<p local-id=3D"28e82cbd5c88">SSL certificate successfully installed</p></li=
>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"7d55a7133ed6"><strong>Postconditions:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"1a2655f1f442">
<li local-id=3D"d1d973745f61">
<p local-id=3D"787dc3e9dc87">Dry-run renewal succeeds</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"da677b4802b1"><strong>Flow of Events:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"d7ff966a4609">
<li local-id=3D"7585ec8af788">
<p local-id=3D"1b9374874559">Run certbot renew --dry-run</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3418ed5169cc">
<p local-id=3D"aacc735cd73c">Confirm success message</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"690bd6507d32"><strong>Alternative Flows:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"3d470d2ea525">
<li local-id=3D"974e2d6b46be">
<p local-id=3D"6d53577285c2">Renewal failure =E2=86=92 Review logs and fix =
configuration</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"7acfe6ed5af9">
<h1 local-id=3D"4d4c2b325552" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.Non-Fu=
nctionalRequirements">4. Non-Functional Requirements</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"c172ce791f39">
<h2 local-id=3D"1c4a101176a0" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.1Perfo=
rmanceRequirements">4.1 Performance Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"4766afd8d3c4">
<li local-id=3D"41146a0915e2">
<p local-id=3D"d7d7616ba9fe">Applications should load within acceptable bro=
wser response time (&lt; 3 seconds).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"41704d08faa8">
<p local-id=3D"08ce754526f8">Apache must handle basic static traffic effici=
ently.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d5c36ebc1a46">
<h2 local-id=3D"bd968b41691e" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.2Secur=
ityRequirements">4.2 Security Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"af5d905c5047">
<li local-id=3D"b0a4c5c935d0">
<p local-id=3D"5988f9c70167">HTTPS must be enforced</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5752a8031d87">
<p local-id=3D"2e4099601582">Valid SSL certificate installed</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"673fe69d5e6c">
<p local-id=3D"190bfb287961">No browser security warnings</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2c42d37eccf2">
<p local-id=3D"7d62b98e85a0">Ports restricted to 22, 80, 443</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4bf6ec70d1da">
<p local-id=3D"f33b08d3af6d">Proper file permissions applied</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"493d6f6c730c">
<h2 local-id=3D"7cdbb83231e6" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.3Usabi=
lityRequirements">4.3 Usability Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"bce740b8b133">
<li local-id=3D"9d8bc73152e1">
<p local-id=3D"b9d07925d2c1">Applications must be accessible via clean subd=
omain URLs</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e65905407ddb">
<p local-id=3D"e3ab124912dc">No manual port specification in browser</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"95b716a7c72d">
<p local-id=3D"e9ae4e2ed8c7">Automatic HTTP =E2=86=92 HTTPS redirection</p>=
</li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"a9442cea990b">
<h2 local-id=3D"f247afb2cfa1" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.4Relia=
bilityRequirements">4.4 Reliability Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"e648ed796835">
<li local-id=3D"409f4f5efecc">
<p local-id=3D"27d415217e56">Apache service must remain active</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"002f58d43412">
<p local-id=3D"779732bc59fd">SSL certificates must auto-renew</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0d31add2d856">
<p local-id=3D"630eb39907d1">DNS must consistently resolve to EC2 IP</p></l=
i>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"a6066bdd7cef">
<h2 local-id=3D"5d11b7d92222" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.5Compl=
ianceRequirements">4.5 Compliance Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"43efb177523f">
<li local-id=3D"74e9b277444c">
<p local-id=3D"42f6d7194510">Follow industry-standard HTTPS implementation<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d34ce8376632">
<p local-id=3D"54e2d1887e9a">Use trusted Certificate Authority (Let=E2=80=
=99s Encrypt)</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"cae5c4e56ecb">
<h1 local-id=3D"72e112cecc92" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-5.Assump=
tionsandDependencies">5. Assumptions and Dependencies</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"9d94d832a5db">
<h2 local-id=3D"3f16b0785a8c" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-5.1Assum=
ptions">5.1 Assumptions</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"2be8f1de2857">
<li local-id=3D"296f701b261e">
<p local-id=3D"f1c1f20be34d">Domain ownership is valid</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e494cc8a4a45">
<p local-id=3D"a3e52fd3cab9">DNS configuration access is available</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8b0578a464b2">
<p local-id=3D"9ddfe414f1bc">EC2 instance has public IP</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"95c2eaa59054">
<h2 local-id=3D"30791d66cfa2" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-5.2Depen=
dencies">5.2 Dependencies</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"40427a59e2ef">
<li local-id=3D"426cc1c330c2">
<p local-id=3D"45c08ee7d077">AWS EC2 availability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6d86f4e0cfa5">
<p local-id=3D"fc6b240f895c">DNS provider availability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8d687945bf70">
<p local-id=3D"1dfeef1654c7">Let=E2=80=99s Encrypt CA availability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"421d6ff78ed4">
<p local-id=3D"8fd60f423ab9">Internet connectivity</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d4fbe4e55368">
<h1 local-id=3D"d556f20923c3" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-6.RiskAn=
alysis">6. Risk Analysis</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"5767a8e8cd41">
<h2 local-id=3D"83ba6902681a" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-6.1RiskI=
dentification">6.1 Risk Identification</h2>
