<hr local-id=3D"ed4fe65bc8a8">
<h2 local-id=3D"797be585ad66" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-6.2RiskM=
itigation">6.2 Risk Mitigation</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"29e273afbba2">
<li local-id=3D"9cb9e9d560aa">
<p local-id=3D"6d17a89f7793">Validate DNS before SSL</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b68aea0b18ad">
<p local-id=3D"734afe547124">Open required ports in security group</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a5a9632993d8">
<p local-id=3D"e2b1cce417c9">Test renewal using dry-run</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"99414f9d5864">
<p local-id=3D"8a661dfdd2c4">Validate Apache configuration using configtest=
</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d0d7e924cb40">
<h1 local-id=3D"ef3bec20787d" id=3D"T6-RequirementAnalysisDocument-7.Glossa=
ry">7. Glossary</h1>
